OL,7,FTransport Secretary, Mark Harper, has
OL,8,Fruled out reinstating hard shoulders
OL,9,Fon existing smart motorways, claiming
OL,10,Fthat it would reduce capacity and
OL,11,F"drive up casualties" on the road
OL,12,Fnetwork.
OL,14,FThe Government announced on Monday
OL,15,Fthat it was scrapping plans for new
OL,16,Fsmart motorways at 14 sites across
OL,17,Fthe UK, citing cost pressures and a
OL,18,Flack of public confidence in the
OL,19,Ftechnology.
OL,3,CMinister refuses to re-install hard
OL,4,Cshoulders on smart motorways and
OL,5,Cinsists they're still safe
